                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I ask the right hon. Gentleman whether he considers that this outrage indicates the existence of any widespread system of anti-British propaganda in Iraq?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-76953ff9-7aa8-498e-acc4-0d0c6e0cd56c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-04-05/debates/f1e3b5be-b055-4814-a6ed-d49c995115b9/Iraq(MurderOfBritishConsul)#contribution-76953ff9-7aa8-498e-acc4-0d0c6e0cd56c">
